sentences.english: HIV stands for human immunodeficiency virus.
sentences.chinese: 艾滋病病毒是指人體免疫缺損病毒。

sentences.english: PHB is one of the ideal scaffold material in bone tissue engineering.
sentences.chinese: PHB可以作爲組織工程材料中的一種來修復骨缺損。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate the method for the treatment of soft tissue defect on the heel.
sentences.chinese: 目的探討足跟部軟組織缺損的治療方法。

sentences.english: Tissue engineered bone had good ability to repair large segment tibia defect of Caprine.
sentences.chinese: 組織工程骨具有良好的修復山羊大段骨缺損的能力。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate the relationship between tooth occlusive contact in the laterotrusion and wedge-shaped defects.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究牙頸部楔狀缺損與牙齒咬合接觸的關係。

sentences.english: Conclusion The gingival recession and the wedge shaped defect are common dental diseases in the elderly.
sentences.chinese: 結論牙齦退縮與楔狀缺損是中老年人常見的牙病。

sentences.english: Objective To probe the enlargement of using range of vascularized fibular transferring.
sentences.chinese: 目的探索擴大吻合血管腓骨移植修復骨缺損的範圍。

sentences.english: The results of removal alone were dependent on the size of the defect in the capitellum .
sentences.chinese: 而骨片切除的效果取決於肱骨小頭缺損的大小。

sentences.english: Objective To evaluate clinical effect of composite inlays in the defective molars.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察複合樹脂嵌體修復磨牙缺損的臨牀療效。

sentences.english: To evaluate the effectiveness of self-etching bond system in repair of sphenoid defects.
sentences.chinese: 目的評價自酸蝕粘接修復楔狀缺損的效果。

sentences.english: Barium radiography showed there were filling defect, niche, bridging fold, etc.
sentences.chinese: 鋇劑造影表現是充盈缺損，龕影和橋形皺襞等。

sentences.english: AIDS is an acronym for"Acquired Immune Deficiency Syndrome."
sentences.chinese: 艾滋病的全稱是“獲得性免疫缺損綜合徵”。

sentences.english: In case of big defect, anterior rectus sheath flap was placed in addition.
sentences.chinese: 腹直肌前鞘翻轉成形可補充修補巨大缺損。

sentences.english: To reconstruct the osseous defect, we prefer the fibula as the emphasis is on compression strength.
sentences.chinese: 爲重建骨性缺損，我們更喜歡用腓骨作爲抗壓的重點。

sentences.english: At 2 weeks after fresh autogenous bone grafted, there was some new callus in bone defection.
sentences.chinese: 新鮮骨塊植入後第2周，骨缺損處可見新生骨。

sentences.english: The flap is suitable to repair tissue defect of sole of the foot.
sentences.chinese: 手術操作簡便，是修復足跟部皮膚缺損的理想皮瓣。
